orrespContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L00463">Schnitzler an Bahr, 17. 7. 1895</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L00465">Bahr an Schnitzler, 23. 7. 1895</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00462">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 10. 7. 1895</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00467">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 28. 7. 1895</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
